Netflix SQL Analysis Project

Project Overview

This project focuses on analyzing a Netflix-style dataset using MySQL Workbench to gain valuable business insights through SQL. The analysis explores content distribution, ratings, countries, release trends, and other key metrics by applying SQL concepts commonly used in real-world data analytics.

Business Objective

The objective of this project is to analyze Netflix content data and answer business-related questions that help understand content availability, popularity, geographical distribution, and release patterns using SQL.

Dataset Information

* Dataset: Generated Netflix Dataset
* Total Records: 1,000
* Total Columns: 12

