Business Analysis Performed

* Compared the distribution of Movies and TV Shows.
* Identified countries producing the highest amount of content.
* Analyzed the most common content ratings.
* Examined content release trends across different years.
* Identified the newest and oldest titles in the dataset.
* Ranked content using SQL window functions.
* Performed aggregations and filtering to answer business questions.
* Generated insights using advanced SQL queries.

